For kafka - 

$ cd /usr/local/etc/zookeeper

Tab 1:
$ zookeeper-server-start /usr/local/etc/kafka/zookeeper.properties

Tab 2:
$ kafka-server-start /usr/local/etc/kafka/server.properties

Tab 3:
$ kafka-console-producer broker-list localhost:9093 --topic test

Tab 4:
$ kafka-console-consumer --bootstrap-server localhost:9093 --topic test

Tab 5:
-- For this practice project
$ kafka-console-consumer --bootstrap-server localhost:9093 --topic allAboutUsersTopic







